{"id":261269,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/11/维权网-安徽肥东县刘丰业赴京上访被押回殴打（/","date":"2012-11-05T16:46:10Z","modified":"2012-11-05T16:46:10Z","title":"维权网 | 安徽肥东县刘丰业赴京上访被押回殴打（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a><span>（维权网信息员周维林报道）安徽省合肥市肥东县上访维权者刘丰业为生存权于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">29</span><span>日</span><span>赴京上访，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span>日中午</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">12</span><span>时</span><span>许给本网信息员电话，称被北京警方控制，关押于一处场所，正等待地方维稳人员来接，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>日晚</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">21</span><span>时许被维稳人员押回合肥送回住宅，而</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span>日晚</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">18</span><span>时被三名自称信访局的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">30</span><span>多岁的男子入宅殴打。</span></p>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>据刘丰业称，他于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span>日</span><span>在军事博物馆附近被数名警察查验身份证后，被警方带到一处房屋关押，其后有合肥市驻京办的人通知其户籍所在的村委会来人，维稳人员于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>日</span><span>将刘丰业从北京乘火车带回，送他到肥东县八斗镇的住处。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span>日晚</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">18</span><span>时</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">40</span><span>分</span><span>许，有三名自称肥东县信访局的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">30</span><span>多岁男子驾车到刘丰业住处，对刘丰业一阵拳打脚踢，口称是因为刘丰业赴京上访才来打的，打完后扬长而去。其后刘丰业报警，肥东县公安局八斗派出所于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">19</span><span>时</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">20</span><span>分出警，给刘丰业做了笔录，然后刘丰业被亲戚送花张医院住院治疗。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>刘丰业为民办教师办理养老保险一事多次上访无果，据刘丰业称他了解到有些从事民办教师年数比他少得多的人都办理了，他符合条件却没办理，跑了无数次肥东县信访局、合肥市信访局和安徽省信访局都没有解决，故只得进京上访。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span><br /><span><br /></span></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-TdaooR_JPTM/UJfhWr8tP7I/AAAAAAAAS0A/ivevOYJ-6uM/s1600/%E5%88%98%E4%B8%B0%E4%B8%9A%E5%AE%A1%E6%89%B9%E8%A1%A8.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-TdaooR_JPTM/UJfhWr8tP7I/AAAAAAAAS0A/ivevOYJ-6uM/s320/%E5%88%98%E4%B8%B0%E4%B8%9A%E5%AE%A1%E6%89%B9%E8%A1%A8.jpg\" width=\"225\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-MFiS4M4k85Q/UJfhcBj88ZI/AAAAAAAAS0I/0LnvIfK8xTI/s1600/P1030456.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"206\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-MFiS4M4k85Q/UJfhcBj88ZI/AAAAAAAAS0I/0LnvIfK8xTI/s320/P1030456.JPG\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p><span><br /></span></div>\n</div>\n<div><img width=\"1\" height=\"1\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/751033951089627103-6178275949420596788?l=wqw2010.blogspot.com\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=b4fd4ae247\">\n<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/mstlf\">墙外新闻实时更新 欢迎订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":997,"categories":[18270,18269,20534],"tags":[19196]}